                  <li>• Why using one adds value</li>
                  <li>• The process of hiring one (with tips & red flags)</li>
                  <li>• Important cost considerations</li>
                  <li>• How to manage vendor relationships and oversight</li>
                  <li>• A step-by-step timeline</li>
                  <li>• FAQs — and much more</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
